==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: (A place or circumstance where) people do not resemble people, and ghosts do not resemble ghosts.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén bù xìang rén, gŭi bù xìang gŭi

===Adjective===
'''[[人]][[不]][[像]][[人]]，[[鬼]][[不]][[像]][[鬼]]'''

# [[ghastly]]

#: ''[[我]][[过]][[了]][[四]][[年]]'''人不像人鬼不像鬼'''[[的]][[生活]].'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[我]][[過]][[了]][[四]][[年]]'''人不像人鬼不像鬼'''[[的]][[生活]].'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

